1
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:56,400
Dismissed.

2
00:00:58,460 --> 00:00:59,390
Archivist Shen,

3
00:00:59,800 --> 00:01:00,800
I've wronged you.

4
00:01:01,330 --> 00:01:02,500
If not done this way,

5
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:03,660
Qin Muzhi

6
00:01:03,860 --> 00:01:05,099
and my third brother's spies

7
00:01:05,099 --> 00:01:06,160
would surely notice.

8
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:07,660
Your Highness invited me late at night.

9
00:01:07,660 --> 00:01:08,720
What is the matter?

10
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:14,330
This is the token to enter Tianji Pavilion.

11
00:01:14,330 --> 00:01:15,930
I know you are investigating

12
00:01:16,060 --> 00:01:17,600
the truth behind the dragon vein soul-devouring.

13
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:19,260
Tianji Pavilion is a key link.

14
00:01:20,660 --> 00:01:21,789
Your Highness knows

15
00:01:21,830 --> 00:01:23,030
a lot about this case.

16
00:01:24,100 --> 00:01:25,030
My birth mother

17
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:28,500
died of illness years ago for opposing the dragon vein plan.

18
00:01:28,500 --> 00:01:30,300
I investigated secretly for years,

19
00:01:30,300 --> 00:01:32,900
only to find the plan led by the Imperial Astronomy Bureau,

20
00:01:32,900 --> 00:01:34,160
executed by Qin Muzhi,

21
00:01:34,229 --> 00:01:37,289
with my third brother providing funds and protection.

22
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:40,830
This thumb ring and your jade pendant are a pair.

23
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:44,200
The three tokens were meant to verify and restrict each other.

24
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,130
Unfortunately,

25
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,800
Xiao Chong'an was murdered,

26
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,360
Gu Wenyuan went missing,

27
00:01:49,430 --> 00:01:51,490
and Shen Qingshan's fate is unknown.

28
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:53,090
Why help me, Your Highness?

29
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:58,000
I need you to get evidence from Tianji Pavilion

30
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,660
to bring down my third brother and Qin Muzhi.

31
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,460
You need my protection and intelligence.

32
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,530
We both get what we want.

33
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:40,160
Mercury as a river,

34
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,490
cinnabar as a boundary.

35
00:02:52,660 --> 00:02:53,630
Xiao Chong'an's

36
00:02:54,930 --> 00:02:56,530
last struggle before death.

37
00:03:08,900 --> 00:03:10,930
Director of the Imperial Astronomy Bureau.

38
00:03:10,930 --> 00:03:11,860
It really is him.

39
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:25,660
Those who trespass Tianji Pavilion

40
00:03:25,660 --> 00:03:27,500
will leave their souls here.

41
00:03:35,829 --> 00:03:37,430
Controlled by silk threads.

42
00:03:45,530 --> 00:03:47,390
Illusions based on light and fog,

43
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:49,100
combined with hallucinogenic drugs.

44
00:03:49,100 --> 00:03:50,660
The arm is a mechanical prosthesis.

45
00:03:50,660 --> 00:03:52,160
The soul puppets move in unison,

46
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,630
controlled by the same core.

47
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:54,260
Upstairs.

48
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:13,000
Qingshan's son.

49
00:04:14,130 --> 00:04:15,930
You are finally here.

50
00:04:16,329 --> 00:04:17,160
Senior Xiao.

51
00:04:18,230 --> 00:04:20,459
Were you killed by the Director of the Imperial Astronomy Bureau?

52
00:04:20,459 --> 00:04:21,260
The Director,

53
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:22,430
Xuan Zhenzi,

54
00:04:23,100 --> 00:04:24,630
wanted to use the dragon vein soul-devouring formation

55
00:04:24,630 --> 00:04:25,760
to devour the soul power of 49

56
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,620
people with special birthdates.

57
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:28,560
I opposed,

58
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,260
had my soul extracted to make a puppet,

59
00:04:30,260 --> 00:04:31,590
to guard this pavilion.

60
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,000
The star map is inverted.

61
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:34,659
The center is not the North Pole,

62
00:04:34,659 --> 00:04:35,560
but

63
00:04:36,030 --> 00:04:38,130
the ninth floor of the Imperial Astronomy Bureau's Black Tower.

64
00:04:38,130 --> 00:04:38,659
There

65
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:40,390
is the formation's core

66
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,130
and

67
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,030
the entrance to the dragon vein.

68
00:04:43,030 --> 00:04:45,130
So Tianji Pavilion is just an observation node.

69
00:04:45,130 --> 00:04:47,190
The real dragon vein devouring souls

70
00:04:48,060 --> 00:04:50,630
is underground at the Imperial Astronomy Bureau.

71
00:04:50,630 --> 00:04:52,060
The ninth floor of the Black Tower

72
00:04:52,060 --> 00:04:52,860
is not a tower,

73
00:04:53,100 --> 00:04:53,730
but a well.

74
00:04:54,300 --> 00:04:56,659
It leads to the dragon vein spiritual point below.

75
00:04:56,659 --> 00:04:58,120
The Director sits within,

76
00:04:58,659 --> 00:04:59,900
close to success.

77
00:05:04,030 --> 00:05:05,160
Destroy my core,

78
00:05:05,660 --> 00:05:06,360
otherwise

79
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:08,000
I can't control it.

80
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:14,430
Drawn by the Director's essence blood.

81
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:16,260
This is the hub that controls all the ghosts.

82
00:05:16,260 --> 00:05:17,630
Destroy it,

83
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:19,530
so I can be freed,

84
00:05:20,230 --> 00:05:24,730
and you can see the real evidence I left behind.

85
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:45,200
Father.

86
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:47,900
It is indeed inside the Directorate of Astronomy.

87
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:48,360
Mo'er,

88
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,130
keep this jade safe.

89
00:05:50,430 --> 00:05:51,890
If I do not return in a year,

90
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:52,760
take it

91
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:55,320
and find your Uncle Lu and Uncle Xiao.

92
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,430
They will tell you what to do.

93
00:05:57,430 --> 00:05:58,560
Where are you going?

94
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:02,830
To find the deepest secret of this dynasty.

95
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:25,730
Nephew Shen,

96
00:06:26,330 --> 00:06:27,460
you've worked hard.

97
00:06:27,930 --> 00:06:29,330
Did you get the evidence?

98
00:06:30,730 --> 00:06:32,060
Lord Qin is indeed here.

99
00:06:35,900 --> 00:06:37,300
I've been following you.

100
00:06:37,460 --> 00:06:38,060
Now,

101
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,430
give me the parchment and the jade tablet.

102
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:42,260
I'll take you to see your father.

103
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,960
By the Emperor's verbal decree,

104
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:46,260
Registrar Shen Mo of the Penal Department has done well in solving the case.

105
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:47,830
He is hereby promoted to Vice Director of the Directorate of Astronomy.

106
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:49,890
He is to take up the post immediately.

107
00:06:53,430 --> 00:06:54,500
It seems

108
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:56,100
the Director

109
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,600
can't wait to see you.
